title.narrative: Banking & Financial Services - El Salvador. Banking & Financial Services -El Salvador. Banking and Financial Services - Deposit Insurance. Deposit Insurance - Banking and Financial Services

description.narrative: Support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy, most importantly financial intermediation – the efficient generation and allocation of savings to their most productive use.

This award strives to support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy. More specifically, this includes Intermittent advisor is providing technical assistance to the Instituto de Garantia de depositos of El Salvador in updating their legal framework to adapt their deposit insurance scheme and resolution process to the Internationally accepted best practices such as the IADI Core Principles for Effective Deposit Insurance Systems and the Key Attributes of Effective Resolution Frameworks.. Award Description - Project was discontinued and broken into individual country-specific projects. Intermittent advisors assist Central Banks in strengthening the capacity of its deposit insurance agencies in line with internationally recognized Core Principles of Deposit Insurance, allowing the deposit insurance system to better guarantee financial stability.. Projects have been re-started under country-specific workplans.
